    <p>If searching for a specific topic, the <xref ref="index-page" text="title"/> or the embedded search bar at the top of the page will be of use.</p>
    <p>In the next chapter, <xref ref="gettingstarted" text="title"/>, the various tools and features of this book will be introduced and explained.</p>
